Local setup

project_dir
|_grav-admin
| |_user (symlink)
|_user  
| |_grav-theme (symlink)
|_grav-theme

SYMLINKS - (Vince's Desktop)

Webroot to Grav install
mklink /D D:\dev\xampp\htdocs\wheat D:\dev\_PROJECTS\wheat\grav-admin

Grav-admin user folder to project user
mklink /D D:\dev\_PROJECTS\wheat\grav-admin\user D:\dev\_PROJECTS\wheat\user

user/themes/project-theme to grav-theme-name
mklink /D D:\dev\_PROJECTS\wheat\user\themes\wheat D:\dev\_PROJECTS\wheat\grav-theme-wheat


SYMLINKS (Vince's - Laptop)

Webroot to Grav install
mklink /D C:\xampp\htdocs\wheat C:\Users\vincent\_calotte\wheat\grav-admin

Grav-admin user folder to project user
mklink /D C:\Users\vincent\_calotte\wheat\grav-admin\user C:\Users\vincent\_calotte\wheat\user

user/themes/project-theme to grav-theme-name
mklink /D C:\Users\vincent\_calotte\wheat\user\themes\wheat C:\Users\vincent\_calotte\wheat\grav-theme-wheat
